---
title: Mushroom and Cheese Baked Tacos with salsa and smashed avocado
description: These DIY crunchy shelled tacos are filled with hearty beans, creamy avocado and oozing melted cheese. Serve hot from the oven and get ready for a fiesta of flavours.
